<%- include("partials/header") -%>

<section class="lightSection">
  <div>
    <h1 class="swingvasion-title">Event Passes and Intensive Prices</h1>

    <div class="mb-3">
      <div class="swingvasion-box">
        <div class="swingvasion-details">
          <div class="m-4">
            <p>All passes include:</p>

            <ul style="font-size: 18px">
              <li>All workshops of your level</li>
              <li>Friday and Saturday night parties and Sunday tea dance</li>
              <li>Friday and Saturday shows</li>
              <li>Competition entry fees</li>
            </ul>

            <em>All prices are quoted in New Zealand dollars.</em>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="swingvasion-box">
        <div class="swingvasion-details">
          <div class="m-4">
            <h3 class="p-0 mt-4">LOCAL FULL PASS</h3>

            <ul style="font-size: 18px">
              <li>
                Early bird price: $270 (Early bird pricing ends 9 December 2026)
              </li>
              <li>Full ticket price: $290</li>
            </ul>

            <em
              >Early bird pricing is only applicable if full payment is received
              before the listed end date.</em
            >
          </div>

          <div class="m-4">
            <h3 class="p-0 mt-4">INTERNATIONAL PASS</h3>
            <p>
              Only valid for those established and residing outside of New
              Zealand.
            </p>

            <ul style="font-size: 18px">
              <li>International pass price: $250</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="m-4">
            <h3 class="p-0 mt-4">FIRST TIMER PASS</h3>
            <p>
              For those who have been dancing WCS less than 12 months and this
              is their first WSDC event.
            </p>

            <ul style="font-size: 18px">
              <li>First timer pass price: $230</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="m-4">
            <h3 class="p-0 mt-4">ALL STAR PASS</h3>
            <p>
              For dancers eligible to dance in the WSDC All Star division and
              above.
            </p>

            <ul style="font-size: 18px">
              <li>All Star pass price: FREE</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="swingvasion-box">
        <div class="swingvasion-details">
          <div class="m-4">
            <h3 class="p-0 mt-4">BRAD'S WHIMSICALITY INTENSIVE</h3>
            <p>
              Musicality doesn’t have to be so technical. This intensive
              explores high level musicality concepts and simplifies them,
              making them easier for dancers of all levels to digest… and maybe
              even have a little fun along the way.
            </p>

            <ul style="font-size: 18px">
              <li>Intensive price: $60</li>
            </ul>

            <em
              >NOTE: Brad’s intensive is an additional cost and not included in
              any of the weekend passes.</em
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="swingvasion-box">
        <div class="swingvasion-details">
          <div class="m-4">
            <h2>CANCELLATION POLICY</h2>

            <ul style="font-size: 18px">
              <li>
                Change of mind - We acknowledge that sometimes life means things
                do change. Swingvasion will offer a full refund if you are no
                longer able to attend, no questions asked, provided we are
                notified a minimum of 4 weeks prior to the event commencement.
              </li>
              <li>
                Illness/injury - We understand illness and injury is often
                beyond control. Please help us to keep you and other
                participants safe and do not attend if you become unwell. Please
                contact us directly, where Swingvasion will use fair and
                reasonable discretion to offer appropriate refunds.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="swingvasion-box">
        <div class="swingvasion-details">
          <div class="m-4">
            <h2>REGISTRATION POLICY</h2>

            <p style="font-size: 18px">
              By registering for this event you expressly grant the director(s)
              of Swingvasion Ltd and it’s assignees, licensees, vendors, and
              legal representatives the unlimited right and authority to use
              your name and any photograph or video recording of your
              participation at Swingvasion in any and all media, in whatever
              manner, for any lawful purpose, without any obligation to you. You
              further agree for yourself, your heirs, executors, and
              administrators, to waive and release any and all right for damage
              you might have against the Director(s) of Swingvasion Ltd for any
              injuries and damages you may suffer by participating in this event
              and your traveling to and from the event.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") -%>
